---
date: 
  created: {{ end_date.isoformat() }}
description: "{{ posts|length }} posts from {{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}"
hide:
  - navigation
  - toc
---

# {% if logo_url %}<img src="{{ logo_url }}" alt="" style="height:1.2em;vertical-align:middle"> {% endif %}{{ feed_name }} Digest — {{ week_id }}

Posts from **{{ start_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}** to **{{ end_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}**. Total: **{{ posts|length }}** posts.

<!-- more -->

---

{% for post in posts %}

<!-- Post Card -->
## {% if post.author_avatar %} ![avatar of {{ post.author_name }}]({{ post.author_avatar }}){: .avatar style="width:2.2em;height:2.2em;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;vertical-align:middle;" } {% endif %}
**{{ post.author_name }}** [@{{ post.author_handle }}]({{ post.bsky_url }})

<span class="post-meta">{{ post.date }} · :heart: {{ post.likes }} · 💬 {{ post.replies }} · 🔁 {{ post.reposts }}{% if post.language %} · 🌐 {{ post.language }}{% endif %}{% if post.app_source %} · 🛠️ {{ post.app_source }}{% endif %}</span>

{% if post.is_repost %}
!!! info "Repost"
    This is a repost.
{% endif %}

{% if post.is_quote and post.quoted_post %}
!!! quote "Quoted from {{ post.quoted_post.author or 'unknown' }}"
    {{ post.quoted_post.text }}
    [View original]({{ post.quoted_post.uri }})
{% endif %}

{% if post.reply_to %}
<span class="post-meta">In reply to <a href="{{ post.reply_to.url }}">{{ post.reply_to.author or post.reply_to.uri }}</a></span>
{% endif %}

{{ post.text }}

{% if post.embed_images %}
{% for img in post.embed_images %}
![{{ img.alt }}]({{ img.url }}){: .gallery-img }
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if post.embed_links %}
{% for link in post.embed_links %}
{% if link.thumb %}![{{ link.title }}]({{ link.thumb }}){: .link-thumb }{% endif %}
[{{ link.title }}]({{ link.uri }})
{% if link.description %}
> {{ link.description }}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if post.mentions %}
{% for mention in post.mentions %}
<span class="chip">@{{ mention }}</span>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if post.hashtags %}
{% for tag in post.hashtags %}
<span class="chip">#{{ tag }}</span>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if post.links %}
{% for link in post.links %}
<span class="chip"><a href="{{ link }}" target="_blank">{{ link }}</a></span>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if not post.is_public %}
!!! warning "Post not public"
    {% if post.is_deleted %}This post was deleted.{% elif post.is_filtered %}This post was filtered.{% endif %}
{% endif %}

[🔗 View on Bluesky]({{ post.bsky_url }}){:target="_blank" .md-button}


---

{% endfor %}
